{{>layout/home-header}}

<div class="container mt-5">
    {{>layout/bodyheader}}

    <h1 class="text-center mb-5 fw-bold text-primary">공연 예매 관리 시스템</h1>

    <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-2 row-cols-lg-3 g-4">
        <div class="col">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm border-0">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title text-center text-primary fw-bold">회원 관리</h5>
                    <p class="card-text text-center text-muted">새로운 회원을 등록하거나 기존 회원 목록을 관리합니다.</p>
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-2">
                        <a href="/custs/new" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm rounded-pill">회원 가입</a>
                        <a href="/custs" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm rounded-pill">회원 목록</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm border-0">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title text-center text-dark fw-bold">공연 관리</h5>
                    <p class="card-text text-center text-muted">신규 공연을 등록하고, 현재 등록된 공연 목록을 확인합니다.</p>
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-2">
                        <a href="/items/new" class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-sm rounded-pill">공연 등록</a>
                        <a href="/items" class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-sm rounded-pill">공연 목록</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm border-0">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title text-center text-info fw-bold">예매 관리</h5>
                    <p class="card-text text-center text-muted">공연 예매를 처리하고, 예매된 내역을 조회합니다.</p>
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-2">
                        <a href="/bookings/new" class="btn btn-outline-info btn-sm rounded-pill">공연 예매</a>
                        <a href="/bookings" class="btn btn-outline-info btn-sm rounded-pill">예매 내역</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm border-0">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title text-center text-warning fw-bold">문자 발송</h5>
                    <p class="card-text text-center text-muted">예매자들에게 단체 문자를 발송하고 발송 내역을 확인합니다.</p>
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-2">
                        <a href="/sms/send" class="btn btn-outline-warning btn-sm rounded-pill">문자 발송</a>
                        <a href="/sms/sendList" class="btn btn-outline-warning btn-sm rounded-pill">문자 내역</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm border-0">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title text-center text-success fw-bold">SMS 템플릿</h5>
                    <p class="card-text text-center text-muted">문자 발송에 사용할 템플릿을 등록하고 조회합니다.</p>
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-2">
                        <a href="/smsTemplates/new" class="btn btn-outline-success btn-sm rounded-pill">템플릿 등록 및 조회</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    {{>layout/bodyfooter}}
